1
00:00:01,700 --> 00:00:04,560
Previously on Fairy Tail:

2
00:00:04,560 --> 00:00:05,450
I'm Natsu!

3
00:00:05,450 --> 00:00:06,500
I'm Wendy!

4
00:00:06,500 --> 00:00:08,130
And I'm Gajeel, got it?

5
00:00:08,130 --> 00:00:09,900
The three of them together are...

6
00:00:09,900 --> 00:00:12,150
Dragon Slayers, damn it!

7
00:00:09,900 --> 00:00:12,350
Fairy Tail wizards!

8
00:00:09,900 --> 00:00:12,350
The 3 Bestest Friends Group!

9
00:00:12,350 --> 00:00:15,670
Damn, you're not together at all.

10
00:00:16,480 --> 00:00:19,040
Who cares? We beat the King!

11
00:00:19,040 --> 00:00:21,180
And they all lived happily ever after, right?

12
00:00:21,180 --> 00:00:23,110
What happened to my cat?

13
00:00:23,750 --> 00:00:27,720
Uh... But things just took a 
turn for the worse, you know...

14
00:02:16,270 --> 00:02:19,450
Everyone, standing around moping 
isn't going to get us anywhere!

15
00:02:20,580 --> 00:02:24,160
Let's head to the Royal City 
and see if it's true ourselves!

16
00:02:24,630 --> 00:02:27,430
See if... what's true?

17
00:02:27,870 --> 00:02:32,080
About our future.

18
00:02:44,890 --> 00:02:50,490
You must execute me, the one who caused this 
turmoil, in front of the panicking citizens.

19
00:02:50,810 --> 00:02:54,660
As a member of the Royal 
Army... As an Exceed...

20
00:02:55,490 --> 00:02:58,300
Quell the panic, and lead the people.

21
00:02:58,570 --> 00:03:02,660
Become king of a new world, 
without magic power.

22
00:03:03,050 --> 00:03:07,830
How could you seriously say 
such nonsense, Prince?!

23
00:03:16,600 --> 00:03:18,460
Bye-bye, Edolas.

24
00:03:31,980 --> 00:03:35,650
If I wasn't prepared to die, I 
wouldn't have gone through with this.

25
00:03:37,910 --> 00:03:40,360
I refuse! This is foolishness!

26
00:03:41,480 --> 00:03:43,390
Why must I kill you?

27
00:03:46,990 --> 00:03:48,410
There is no way I could do it.

28
00:03:49,320 --> 00:03:51,020
No, you are capable of doing it.

29
00:03:51,020 --> 00:03:53,230
And what do you know about me?

30
00:03:55,050 --> 00:04:00,130
As an Exceed, you saved my life as a child.

31
00:04:01,570 --> 00:04:06,730
You are a man who knows how precious life 
is, regardless of the race one belongs to.

32
00:04:07,100 --> 00:04:11,800
And you're telling me to keep living 
my life bearing that cross on my back?!

33
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:15,770
You are the only one strong 
enough to overcome that.

34
00:04:16,380 --> 00:04:19,960
Please understand... Someone has to do it.

35
00:04:20,290 --> 00:04:24,280
Then do it yourself. 
You're suited to be king.

36
00:04:25,430 --> 00:04:27,950
I brought the world to ruin!

37
00:04:27,950 --> 00:04:30,040
You did it thinking it was for the best.

38
00:04:30,870 --> 00:04:33,010
Now is the time we need 
someone with your will,

39
00:04:33,010 --> 00:04:37,460
strong enough to risk your own 
life for the sake of Edolas!

40
00:04:39,650 --> 00:04:43,950
If you brought the world to 
ruin, then take responsibility!

41
00:04:44,250 --> 00:04:46,010
And you don't do that by dying.

42
00:04:46,310 --> 00:04:49,100
You do it by leading the world once again!

43
00:04:52,330 --> 00:04:54,910
But that won't stop this panic...

44
00:04:56,170 --> 00:04:58,240
Mommy, I'm scared...

45
00:04:58,240 --> 00:05:01,150
It'll be okay... Everything'll be okay...

46
00:05:07,650 --> 00:05:09,660
Don't panic! Stay calm!

47
00:05:10,390 --> 00:05:13,870
What are you, nuts? This 
is no time to be calm!

48
00:05:13,870 --> 00:05:15,480
Hurry up and run away yourself!

49
00:05:16,650 --> 00:05:19,660
Run away? Run away to where?!

50
00:05:20,740 --> 00:05:21,970
Daddy!

51
00:05:21,970 --> 00:05:23,070
Are you okay?

52
00:05:23,070 --> 00:05:24,920
Don't let your eyes off your kid!

53
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:45,940
I'll be the villain.

54
00:05:54,470 --> 00:05:56,190
Extalia is...

55
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:58,240
Our house...

56
00:05:58,770 --> 00:06:01,500
The home he had to return to...

57
00:06:01,500 --> 00:06:04,710
Damn it! Damn it all!

58
00:06:06,340 --> 00:06:10,040
I was banished from Extalia,

59
00:06:10,500 --> 00:06:12,730
and threw my lot in with the humans.

60
00:06:14,940 --> 00:06:18,510
But for this incident, 
I betrayed the Kingdom,

61
00:06:18,910 --> 00:06:21,150
and I have no place to return to now.

62
00:06:22,080 --> 00:06:25,820
I will become the great 
villain and be executed...

63
00:06:25,820 --> 00:06:26,910
No, you will not!

64
00:06:28,880 --> 00:06:32,520
You saved my life. I cannot allow you to die.

65
00:06:33,210 --> 00:06:35,870
I must give you happiness.

66
00:06:36,870 --> 00:06:40,710
And I say the exact same thing to you.

67
00:06:42,570 --> 00:06:45,510
If either one of us takes 
responsibility and is killed,

68
00:06:45,510 --> 00:06:47,780
nothing will come of it except unhappiness.

69
00:06:48,270 --> 00:06:51,600
Then how do we calm the people?

70
00:06:53,940 --> 00:06:55,270
Was it a foolish plan?

71
00:06:56,490 --> 00:06:59,050
Panther Lily-sama, we have a big problem!

72
00:06:59,310 --> 00:07:04,060
We know. As you can see, the Anima...

73
00:07:04,060 --> 00:07:06,360
You're trying to stop it, right?

74
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:08,570
No, that's not it.

75
00:07:08,570 --> 00:07:12,010
Anyway, there are people wreaking 
havoc in the castle city.

76
00:07:12,010 --> 00:07:14,740
Cities are being destroyed 
one after another...

77
00:07:16,550 --> 00:07:19,210
The panic seems worse 
than even I predicted...

78
00:07:19,950 --> 00:07:21,770
We have to do something soon, or...

79
00:07:22,280 --> 00:07:24,700
First, we have to stop the rioting.

80
00:07:24,700 --> 00:07:28,250
Yes. We must strike before 
it spreads further.

81
00:07:28,530 --> 00:07:31,140
Um... And you are?

82
00:07:56,250 --> 00:07:57,400
How many people are rioting?

83
00:07:57,400 --> 00:07:59,340
T-Three people!

84
00:07:59,340 --> 00:08:00,690
Just three people?

85
00:08:01,020 --> 00:08:02,120
Why haven't you stopped them?

86
00:08:02,120 --> 00:08:05,420
W-Well, they're really strong, and...

87
00:08:15,100 --> 00:08:17,770
I am the Great Demon King Dragneel!

88
00:08:17,770 --> 00:08:21,730
I've taken all this world's magic power!

89
00:08:21,730 --> 00:08:22,230
N...!

90
00:08:22,650 --> 00:08:23,690
Natsu!

91
00:08:25,100 --> 00:08:27,230
S-Save us!

92
00:08:28,820 --> 00:08:31,030
What are you doing, me?

93
00:08:32,370 --> 00:08:33,320
Er...

94
00:08:36,650 --> 00:08:42,150
I'm the one... who beat your king!

95
00:08:43,800 --> 00:08:47,140
Maybe I'll let him live 
just as a special favor!

96
00:08:49,210 --> 00:08:50,270
Your Highness!

97
00:08:50,680 --> 00:08:51,720
The King...

98
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:53,010
How terrible!

99
00:08:54,190 --> 00:08:56,850
Redfox! Marvel!

100
00:08:56,850 --> 00:09:00,680
Destroy the city, my loyal servants!

101
00:09:08,480 --> 00:09:10,110
Who the hell's this guy?

102
00:09:10,110 --> 00:09:11,690
His arm turned into a sword!

103
00:09:11,690 --> 00:09:12,740
The city!

104
00:09:15,480 --> 00:09:18,940
That's a great villain who is 
trying to destroy this city!

105
00:09:18,940 --> 00:09:22,000
They are truly a group bent on doing evil!

106
00:09:33,800 --> 00:09:35,250
I'm sorry...

107
00:09:35,250 --> 00:09:38,220
Just look! This is all their doing!

108
00:09:45,060 --> 00:09:46,900
What are you doing?

109
00:09:46,900 --> 00:09:47,730
Stop this!

110
00:09:48,240 --> 00:09:51,230
Destroy more of the city!

111
00:09:51,230 --> 00:09:52,730
My servants!

112
00:09:53,290 --> 00:09:56,310
Shut up with the "servant" 
thing already, you jerk!

113
00:09:56,310 --> 00:09:58,200
Whatever, just do it!

114
00:09:58,200 --> 00:10:00,260
He's talking like he's hot stuff...

115
00:10:01,720 --> 00:10:03,860
They're... Don't tell me...

116
00:10:03,860 --> 00:10:07,970
It's them! They're the ones that 
stole the magic power from Edolas!

117
00:10:07,970 --> 00:10:09,650
The Great Demon King Dragneel!

118
00:10:09,650 --> 00:10:10,820
That's right!

119
00:10:10,820 --> 00:10:14,030
He is the great villain who 
has stolen away our happiness!

120
00:10:14,030 --> 00:10:16,380
How dare you! Give us back our magic power!

121
00:10:16,380 --> 00:10:18,460
I don't like the sound of that...

122
00:10:18,460 --> 00:10:21,350
Every person who resists me is...

123
00:10:22,660 --> 00:10:23,730
What's that?

124
00:10:23,730 --> 00:10:24,550
Fire's coming from his mouth!

125
00:10:24,550 --> 00:10:25,970
M-Monster!

126
00:10:26,390 --> 00:10:28,980
Stop this, Natsu!

127
00:10:30,570 --> 00:10:31,890
Who was that?

128
00:10:31,890 --> 00:10:34,100
Over there, in the castle!

129
00:10:34,100 --> 00:10:35,230
Who is that?

130
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:41,070
I am the Great Demon King Dragneel.

131
00:10:41,700 --> 00:10:43,300
Stop this foolishness!

132
00:10:43,650 --> 00:10:45,240
The King has fallen!

133
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:47,580
There is no need to attack the Royal City...

134
00:10:47,850 --> 00:10:49,750
Fire!

135
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:50,920
Stop this!

136
00:10:52,800 --> 00:10:58,130
Can you stop me, Prince of Edolas?

137
00:10:58,550 --> 00:10:59,750
Prince?

138
00:10:59,750 --> 00:11:01,120
Did he just say prince?

139
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:03,880
He went missing 7 years ago...

140
00:11:04,360 --> 00:11:05,760
Prince Jellal!

141
00:11:06,290 --> 00:11:09,000
Impossible... That can't actually be him!

142
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:10,690
W-What do you think?

143
00:11:10,690 --> 00:11:12,300
I can't believe it!

144
00:11:12,300 --> 00:11:14,510
Why are they here?

145
00:11:15,490 --> 00:11:18,400
I-I let them know.

146
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:20,110
Nady-san!

147
00:11:20,110 --> 00:11:23,360
Since I overheard your conversation...

148
00:11:27,040 --> 00:11:28,190
Come here.

149
00:11:28,950 --> 00:11:32,670
If you don't, there won't be 
a trace left of this city...

150
00:11:34,980 --> 00:11:36,680
Villain and hero...

151
00:11:37,480 --> 00:11:38,340
But...

152
00:11:38,950 --> 00:11:40,730
What happened to the Magic Regiments?

153
00:11:40,730 --> 00:11:42,700
The King's gonna be killed at this rate!

154
00:11:42,700 --> 00:11:45,700
Is that person he called 
the Prince the real one?

155
00:11:45,700 --> 00:11:48,870
What does it matter? There's no 
way he could beat that monster!

156
00:11:48,870 --> 00:11:51,830
The people do not have 
trust in you yet, Prince.

157
00:11:51,830 --> 00:11:54,400
Natsu, don't move from there!

158
00:11:55,210 --> 00:11:56,810
I'm not Natsu.

159
00:11:57,050 --> 00:11:59,000
I'm the Great Demon King Dragneel.

160
00:12:00,570 --> 00:12:03,970
He might be trying to give the Prince 
some heroics with this silly act,

161
00:12:04,620 --> 00:12:09,660
but when it comes to light that he's just 
faking being beaten, there'll be no turning back.

162
00:12:10,220 --> 00:12:13,160
Don't tell me he really plans on dying?!

163
00:12:13,160 --> 00:12:17,230
Y-You should be prepared yourself.

164
00:12:17,230 --> 00:12:22,220
Prepared for what's about to happen... to us.

165
00:12:32,700 --> 00:12:34,270
I'm back to normal!

166
00:12:34,270 --> 00:12:37,390
W-What's this? You're so heavy!

167
00:12:37,390 --> 00:12:40,130
Men!

168
00:12:41,260 --> 00:12:43,970
What in the world is going on?

169
00:12:43,970 --> 00:12:45,780
Is that magic power?

170
00:12:46,190 --> 00:12:50,340
Queen? Queen, are you okay?!

171
00:12:50,740 --> 00:12:53,050
Men!

172
00:13:02,120 --> 00:13:03,740
That's the Prince!

173
00:13:03,740 --> 00:13:06,600
Does he plan on fighting 
with that Demon King person?

174
00:13:06,600 --> 00:13:08,890
But he's up against a fire-breathing monster!

175
00:13:08,890 --> 00:13:10,550
Prince? Him?

176
00:13:11,510 --> 00:13:15,390
Fool! I know what you're trying to do...

177
00:13:15,390 --> 00:13:19,060
But there's no way to bring 
things under control!

178
00:13:30,370 --> 00:13:31,600
Sleep!

179
00:13:34,810 --> 00:13:36,960
The magic power is being 
sucked into the Anima...

180
00:13:38,520 --> 00:13:41,670
What's wrong? Scared without any magic power?

181
00:13:43,350 --> 00:13:47,970
Yeah, that's right... Magic... is power!

182
00:13:50,140 --> 00:13:51,950
What incredible destructive power!

183
00:13:51,230 --> 00:13:52,930
Is that the power of magic?

184
00:13:53,340 --> 00:13:54,120
Don't!

185
00:13:54,800 --> 00:13:57,300
Natsu-san, you're going too far!

186
00:13:57,300 --> 00:13:58,270
It's fine...

187
00:13:58,820 --> 00:14:01,910
He's a devil with a huge 
amount of magic power.

188
00:14:01,910 --> 00:14:05,830
And a hero with no magic power 
is going to stand against him.

189
00:14:10,340 --> 00:14:12,000
Enough of this, Natsu.

190
00:14:12,370 --> 00:14:14,620
I cannot become a hero.

191
00:14:14,620 --> 00:14:18,660
And you aren't going to get away 
with just pretending to be beaten.

192
00:14:20,660 --> 00:14:21,960
You're on!

193
00:14:23,520 --> 00:14:24,360
Prince!

194
00:14:24,360 --> 00:14:26,520
How violent!

195
00:14:27,980 --> 00:14:29,180
This is a farce!

196
00:14:29,470 --> 00:14:31,840
The people won't come together from this...

197
00:14:32,360 --> 00:14:34,600
No way!

198
00:14:36,370 --> 00:14:37,980
Don't hold back.

199
00:14:41,920 --> 00:14:43,500
Good one, Prince!

200
00:14:43,500 --> 00:14:44,940
Get him!

201
00:14:44,940 --> 00:14:47,140
Please! You can do it!

202
00:14:50,080 --> 00:14:52,230
Looks like we've got a gallery!

203
00:14:52,230 --> 00:14:56,200
You idiot! If you insist on 
doing this, then stay down!

204
00:14:56,200 --> 00:14:57,970
Hell, no!

205
00:14:58,750 --> 00:15:00,300
Prince!

206
00:15:00,900 --> 00:15:02,160
The bastard!

207
00:15:02,160 --> 00:15:03,280
How dare you do that to our Prince!

208
00:15:20,490 --> 00:15:24,440
This is my personal style of a 
Fairy Tail Farewell Ceremony.

209
00:15:25,710 --> 00:15:30,440
There are three conditions I must 
tell someone who leaves Fairy Tail...

210
00:15:30,440 --> 00:15:31,820
One!

211
00:15:32,110 --> 00:15:37,080
You must never reveal sensitive information 
about Fairy Tail to others for as long as you live!

212
00:15:37,080 --> 00:15:38,330
Two!

213
00:15:39,510 --> 00:15:41,020
What was it, again?

214
00:15:41,370 --> 00:15:47,040
You must not have unauthorized contact with 
past clients or profit personally from them!

215
00:15:47,790 --> 00:15:50,020
That's right! Three!

216
00:15:50,690 --> 00:15:55,980
Even if we walk different paths, one must 
always live on as strong as you are able!

217
00:15:57,260 --> 00:16:02,030
You must never treat your own 
life as something insignificant!

218
00:16:02,800 --> 00:16:04,480
You must never forget the friends you love...

219
00:16:05,770 --> 00:16:08,480
...for as long as you live!

220
00:16:19,940 --> 00:16:21,710
Did you get all that?

221
00:16:25,870 --> 00:16:29,420
As long as you keep the guild mindset, 
there's nothing you can't do.

222
00:16:32,640 --> 00:16:35,550
I hope we meet again, Mystogan.

223
00:16:41,710 --> 00:16:42,720
Natsu...

224
00:16:43,520 --> 00:16:45,060
The Prince won!

225
00:16:45,060 --> 00:16:46,680
All right!

226
00:16:47,140 --> 00:16:47,970
Prince!

227
00:16:47,970 --> 00:16:49,660
Wonderful!

228
00:16:52,930 --> 00:16:53,880
Natsu...

229
00:17:13,970 --> 00:17:16,300
Your... Your body...

230
00:17:17,510 --> 00:17:18,620
It's started.

231
00:17:18,620 --> 00:17:21,720
Okay... Let's put on a real 
show as we kick the bucket!

232
00:17:22,280 --> 00:17:23,590
What's this?

233
00:17:23,590 --> 00:17:24,810
The Demon King's body is...

234
00:17:25,310 --> 00:17:27,010
What in the world?

235
00:17:27,330 --> 00:17:32,450
Anima in reverse is removing 
all magic power from Edolas!

236
00:17:32,450 --> 00:17:38,070
And that includes we Exceed and the Dragon 
Slayers, who have a great deal of magic in our bodies!

237
00:17:38,070 --> 00:17:41,240
We're all being swept into Earthland!

238
00:17:41,570 --> 00:17:42,980
What?!

239
00:17:42,980 --> 00:17:47,020
I suspect the Queen understands this.

240
00:17:49,860 --> 00:17:52,040
Queen...

241
00:17:52,040 --> 00:17:53,560
My body...

242
00:17:53,560 --> 00:17:56,430
Don't worry... There's 
nothing to be afraid of.

243
00:17:56,430 --> 00:17:59,910
Edolas has no need for a god any longer.

244
00:18:00,710 --> 00:18:05,600
We must have courage and 
take a new step forward.

245
00:18:06,820 --> 00:18:08,070
W-What?

246
00:18:08,070 --> 00:18:09,520
What's happening?

247
00:18:09,520 --> 00:18:11,980
We're being sucked into the Anima!

248
00:18:21,420 --> 00:18:25,930
I see! That Anima is sucking up 
all the magic power in Edolas!

249
00:18:25,930 --> 00:18:28,640
That means it's going to kick us out, too!

250
00:18:30,480 --> 00:18:32,010
Lucy, Happy!

251
00:18:32,010 --> 00:18:33,240
Natsu!

252
00:18:33,240 --> 00:18:35,170
You're safe, Natsu?

253
00:18:35,620 --> 00:18:36,930
Hey, you!

254
00:18:37,470 --> 00:18:41,490
Magic really is disappearing 
from this world...

255
00:18:41,970 --> 00:18:44,010
Everything is all going to be gone...

256
00:18:44,010 --> 00:18:47,510
What should we do now?

257
00:18:47,510 --> 00:18:50,190
And how is Juvia supposed to know that?

258
00:18:50,730 --> 00:18:52,560
Don't look so glum!

259
00:18:52,900 --> 00:18:56,610
You can't have a guild 
without magic, you say?

260
00:19:00,080 --> 00:19:03,060
As long as you have your friends, 
that's your guild right there!

261
00:19:17,480 --> 00:19:18,740
Scarlet...

262
00:19:19,290 --> 00:19:20,380
Knightwalker...

263
00:19:26,710 --> 00:19:28,630
No... I wish you well...

264
00:19:29,710 --> 00:19:30,620
...Erza.

265
00:19:35,120 --> 00:19:38,060
H-Hey! What in the world?

266
00:19:38,060 --> 00:19:39,570
We're being sucked in!

267
00:19:39,570 --> 00:19:41,180
Men!

268
00:19:41,180 --> 00:19:45,010
I was finally restored, and now what happens?

269
00:19:45,010 --> 00:19:47,370
Nichiya-sama!

270
00:19:58,270 --> 00:20:00,140
D-Don't tell me...

271
00:20:00,540 --> 00:20:03,640
I never would have expected it 
to suck up humans themselves...

272
00:20:05,090 --> 00:20:07,350
The Demon King is floating into the sky!

273
00:20:07,350 --> 00:20:09,760
The Prince saved us all!

274
00:20:09,760 --> 00:20:12,500
Long live the Prince!

275
00:20:13,400 --> 00:20:14,540
Prince!

276
00:20:15,970 --> 00:20:20,010
There is no need to have 
change so immediately.

277
00:20:20,010 --> 00:20:22,610
You should proceed nice and slowly.

278
00:20:23,330 --> 00:20:27,640
Even if it's a walking pace, people 
can still take that first step.

279
00:20:27,880 --> 00:20:30,770
That step towards their future.

280
00:20:34,850 --> 00:20:37,030
Bye-bye, Edo-Lucy!

281
00:20:37,030 --> 00:20:39,250
Bye-bye, other Fairy Tail!

282
00:20:41,510 --> 00:20:44,500
Hey, keep workin' hard, me!

283
00:20:44,500 --> 00:20:46,260
Or wait, you!

284
00:20:46,260 --> 00:20:47,310
I will!

285
00:20:47,310 --> 00:20:50,190
And me, I mean... you, too!

286
00:20:50,190 --> 00:20:52,750
You two are getting me confused...

287
00:20:53,020 --> 00:20:55,600
Bye-bye, Princess!

288
00:20:55,600 --> 00:20:58,320
See you later, everyone!

289
00:20:58,320 --> 00:21:02,340
What are you saying? We'll 
never see them again.

290
00:21:05,020 --> 00:21:07,360
Bye-bye!

291
00:21:07,360 --> 00:21:08,860
You're so pitiful.

292
00:21:09,310 --> 00:21:11,450
Don't go crying now!

293
00:21:12,980 --> 00:21:16,890
And like that, we returned to Earthland.

294
00:21:18,780 --> 00:21:20,900
Farewell, Prince.

295
00:21:22,020 --> 00:21:24,060
Farewell, Lily.

296
00:21:25,430 --> 00:21:28,860
Natsu, Gajeel, Wendy...

297
00:21:29,240 --> 00:21:33,180
And my family... Fairy Tail.

298
00:21:43,990 --> 00:21:47,350
I don't know what happened 
in Edolas after that.

299
00:21:56,640 --> 00:22:00,310
I defeated the Demon King Dragneel!

300
00:22:00,540 --> 00:22:04,930
Even without magic power, 
we humans can still live!

301
00:22:12,160 --> 00:22:15,730
But I believe that everyone 
is still living strong.

302
00:22:17,610 --> 00:22:23,150
Because it's a world where everyone 
knows that precious something.

303
00:23:55,740 --> 00:23:58,330
Right on! We're finally home!

304
00:23:58,330 --> 00:24:00,690
I just hope that everyone 
managed to return safely...

305
00:24:00,690 --> 00:24:03,170
Eh, I'm sure everyone's fine. Don't worry!

306
00:24:03,170 --> 00:24:05,010
What's your basis for that confidence?

307
00:24:05,010 --> 00:24:07,230
Because I believe in everyone in the guild.

308
00:24:07,230 --> 00:24:10,770
And if it comes down to it, 
Gramps'll do something.

309
00:24:10,770 --> 00:24:13,560
Oh, that's actually a pretty sensible answer.

310
00:24:13,840 --> 00:24:15,960
Next time: Lisanna.

311
00:24:16,510 --> 00:24:18,410
What? I'm the same as always!

312
00:24:18,410 --> 00:24:21,390
Something's definitely wrong! You're 
acting all cool for some reason!

313
00:24:21,390 --> 00:24:23,510
D-Don't be silly! N-No, I'm not!

314
00:24:23,510 --> 00:24:25,740


